Van Rompuy Says ‘Plain Hard Work’ Needed to Tackle Debt Crisis

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-10-23T08:22:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/van-rompuy-says-plain-hard-work-needed-to-tackle-debt-crisis.html
European Union President  Herman Van
Rompuy  said “plain hard work” is needed to tackle  Europe ’s
debt crisis.  He spoke today in Brussels at the start of a summit of
European Union heads of state and government.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
